            ✅ 7-Day Money-Back Guarantee
        </div>

        <h2>1. Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with FAQ Chatbot. If you're not happy with our service, we offer a straightforward refund process.</p>

        <h2>2. 7-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2>
        
        <h3>2.1 Eligibility</h3>
        <p>You are eligible for a full refund if:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>You are a <strong>first-time subscriber</strong> (new customer)</li>
            <li>You request a refund within <strong>7 days</strong> of your initial payment</li>
            <li>You have not violated our Terms of Service</li>
            <li>You provide a brief reason for the refund request</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 What's Covered</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Starter Plan - First payment only</li>
            <li>Agency Plan - First payment only</li>
            <li>Enterprise Plan (Lifetime) - Full refund within 7 days</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="example">
            <strong>Example:</strong> You subscribe to the Agency plan on January 1st. You can request a full refund until January 8th (7 days later). After January 8th, the refund guarantee expires.
        </div>

        <h2>3. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
        <p>Refunds are <strong>NOT available</strong> in these cases:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>After the 7-day guarantee period has expired</li>
            <li>For renewal payments (only first payment is covered)</li>
            <li>If your account was terminated for Terms of Service violations</li>
            <li>For partial months (no pro-rated refunds)</li>
            <li>For promotional or discounted subscriptions (50% OFF early bird deals - still eligible for 7-day guarantee)</li>
            <li>If you've been previously refunded for the same plan</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="important">
            <strong>Important:</strong> The 7-day guarantee applies to your FIRST payment only. Subsequent monthly payments are non-refundable.
        </div>

        <h2>4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
        
        <h3>Step-by-Step Process:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Email us:</strong> Send a request to <code>assistly43@gmail.com</code></li>
            <li><strong>Subject Line:</strong> "Refund Request - [Your Email]"</li>
            <li><strong>Include:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your account email address</li>
                    <li>Date of payment</li>
                    <li>Plan you purchased (Starter/Agency/Enterprise)</li>
                    <li>Brief reason for refund (helps us improve)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>We respond:</strong> Within 24-48 hours</li>
            <li><strong>Refund processed:</strong> Within 5-10 business days</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="example">
            <strong>Email Template:</strong><br><br>
            Subject: Refund Request - john@example.com<br><br>
