        <h2>5. Refund Processing Time</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Approval:</strong> Within 24-48 hours of request</li>
            <li><strong>Bank Transfer:</strong> 3-5 business days</li>
            <li><strong>Flutterwave/Card:</strong> 5-10 business days</li>
            <li><strong>PayPal:</strong> 1-3 business days</li>
            <li><strong>Cryptocurrency:</strong> 1-2 business days</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Processing times depend on your payment provider and may vary.</em></p>

        <h2>6. Account Access After Refund</h2>
        <p>Once a refund is processed:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your paid subscription is downgraded to the Free plan</li>
            <li>You lose access to paid features immediately</li>
            <li>Your data is retained for 30 days in case you change your mind</li>
            <li>You can re-subscribe at any time (no additional refund guarantee)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Cancellation vs. Refund</h2>
        
        <h3>7.1 Cancellation (No Refund)</h3>
        <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Go to Dashboard → Settings → Cancel Subscription</li>
            <li>Cancellation takes effect at end of current billing period</li>
            <li>No refund for remaining days in the billing period</li>
            <li>You keep access until the end of the paid period</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>7.2 Refund (Money Back)</h3>
        <p>Request a refund within 7 days:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email assistly43@gmail.com with refund request</li>
            <li>Full payment refunded</li>
            <li>Immediate loss of paid features</li>
            <li>Account downgraded to Free plan</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Promotional/Early Bird Pricing</h2>
        <p>Our current 50% OFF early bird promotion:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Still eligible for 7-day money-back guarantee</li>
            <li>Refund amount: The discounted price you paid</li>
            <li>If you re-subscribe later, early bird pricing may no longer be available</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="example">
            <strong>Example:</strong> You pay $25 (early bird Starter price, normally $49). If you request a refund within 7 days, you get back $25, not $49.
        </div>

        <h2>9. Chargebacks and Disputes</h2>
        <p>We prefer to resolve issues directly:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Contact us before filing a chargeback</li>
            <li>Chargebacks result in immediate account termination</li>
            <li>Chargeback fees may be charged to your account</li>
            <li>We will provide transaction evidence to payment providers</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Please email us first - we're happy to help!</strong></p>

        <h2>10. Technical Issues</h2>
        <p>If you experience service outages or technical problems:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Contact support immediately</li>
            <li>We will extend your subscription to compensate for downtime</li>
            <li>Refunds available for extended outages (>48 hours)</li>
            <li>We maintain 99.9% uptime commitment</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>11. Questions About Refunds</h2>
        <p>Have questions? We're here to help!</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> assistly43@gmail.com</li>
            <li><strong>Subject:</strong> "Refund Policy Question"</li>
            <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 24 hours</li>
